1- Snoop Dogg - Sweat ( David Guetta Remix )

2- Matisse and Sadko - Hi Scandinavia ( Radio edit )

3- Marc Lime & K Bastian - Bizarre ( Michael Mind Remix )

4- Wale - Chillin ( Wideboys Club Mix )( Feat. Lady Gaga )

5- Tiko's Groove feat. Gosha - I Don't Know What To Do

=> The lighting of the map is not default.
